    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, presenting an incredible opportunity for a buyer who wants a like-new experience. The exterior paint is flawless with no scratches or dents, and the interior remains in pristine condition, still smelling fresh and showing zero signs of wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, it is perfect; the engine runs quietly and the transmission shifts seamlessly, exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. Every feature and electronic component works perfectly, making this a rare find for anyone seeking a car in showroom-quality condition.",
      "price": 49500.0,
